<h1>Privacy Policy for Midah Transport Services</h1>
<p>This policy outlines how we handle personal data in compliance with the Malaysia Personal Data Protection Act (PDPA) 2010.</p>
<ul>
    <li><strong>Data Collected:</strong> Student names, parent contact details, and real-time GPS location for transit tracking.</li>
    <li><strong>Purpose:</strong> To provide real-time arrival notifications and ensure student safety during transport.</li>
    <li><strong>Protection:</strong> All data is encrypted and only accessible to authorized transport personnel.</li>
</ul>
<p>Contact us at zen@midahschoolbus.my for data access or deletion requests.</p>